snippet.title: FULL BREAKDOWN of Amber Heard's Legal situation!
snippet.description:
There is a lot of uncertainty when it comes to what is actually going on in the divorce of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. That's why we decided to make a full breakdown of Amber Heard's legal situation for you guys. 
Everything from her allegedly smuggling dogs into Australia to her reportedly being released from the movie AQUAMAN 2.

We hope you enjoy the video, make sure to comment and leave a like if you did!
